red "horns" also resemble the tips of a heart shape.\n\n====Name origin====\nRalts may be a partial {{wp|anagram}} of \'\'astral\'\' (as in {{wp|astral body}}); its other language names seem to follow this. It may also involve \'\'relate\'\', referring to the way Ralts will only relate to kind Trainers. It may also be a play on \'\'{{wp|waltz}}\'\' (a type of dance); Ralts\' evolutionary family appears to have several similarities to dancers.\n\n==In other languages==\n{{Other languages|type=Psychic|type2=Fairy\n|ja=ラルトス \'\'Ralts\'\'|jameaning=From \'\'astral\'\', \'\'relate\'\', and \'\'waltz\'\'\n|fr=Tarsal|frmeaning=Possibly an {{wp|anagram}} of \'\'astral\'\', as in {{wp|astral body}}\n|es=Ralts|esmeaning=Same as English name\n|de=Trasla|demeaning=Possibly an {{wp|anagram}} of \'\'astral\'\', as in {{wp|astral body}}\n|it=Ralts|itmeaning=Same as English name\n|ko=랄토스 \'\'Raltos\'\'|komeaning=Transliteration of its Japanese name\n|zh_cmn=拉魯拉絲 / 拉鲁拉丝 \'\'Lālǔlāsī\'\'|zh_cmnmeaning=Transliteration of its Japanese name\n|ru=Ролтс \'\'Rolts\'\'|rumeaning=Transcription of English name\n}}\n<br clear="left">\n\n==Related articles==\n* [[Rara]]\n* [[Diantha\'s Ralts]]\n\n==External links==\n\n{{-}}\n{{PokémonPrevNext/Head|type=Psychic|type2=Fairy}}\n{{PokémonPrevNext/Pokémon|type=Psychic|prevnum=279|prev=Pelipper|nextnum=281|next=Kirlia}}\n|}\n{{Project Pokédex notice}}\n\n[[Category:Single-type Pokémon|280]]<!--Prior to Gen VI-->\n[[Category:Pokémon that have had their type changed]]\n\n[[de:Trasla]]\n[[es:Ralts]]\n[[fr:Tarsal]]\n[[it:Ralts]]\n[[ja:ラルトス]]\n[[zh:拉鲁拉丝]]'}